sec.p:
To benchmark the performance of the obtained RPs, comparative foam synthesis experiments were carried out using three types of polyols (see Table 2):
A virgin flexible polyether polyol (VP; Alcupol F-4811, Repsol);
A commercially available recycled polyol (CRP; Repsol Reciclex®, Repsol, Puertollano, Spain);
The recovered polyol produced through the process described in this work (RP).
